name: Delta Airlines 767-400 Business Class Lima to Atlanta
description:
Watch this video to see the entire Delta One experience onboard a Boeing 767-400 in Delta Air Line’s International Business Class from Lima, Peru to Atlanta, Georgia! 

You’ll see everything the airline has to offer on one of their premium international routes to Atlanta, their busiest hub. 

This video highlights everything from the Delta Business Class experience! 

You’ll see the Sumaq Lounge you can access in Lima. You’ll even see everything onboard from the impressive Delta catering that highlights some of the finest food in in the air these days, not to mention one of their newest Delta One Business Class Seat. You’ll even see the inflight entertainment from Delta and so much more.
 
0:00 Introduction
1:22 Sumaq Lounge in Lima Airport
2:16 Boarding Delta One 767-400
3:06 Delta One 767-400 Seat Tour
4:27 Delta One Amenities
5:21 Delta One Breakfast
7:40 Delta One 767-400 JebScore
